Guess which Pagani car is Horacio's favourite. The answer's neither Zonda nor Huayra - but, MARA!
He designed and crafted MARA (whose name comes from his parent's initials) when he was 11-12, and still, it is his favourite car. 

Today is the day - the Motor Valley Fest has officially started and will last until Sunday. Come to see live MARA and other Horacio's childhood projects right beside some wonderful Pagani Hypercars. 

#horaciopaganimuseo #pagani #MotorValley @motorvalleyofficial #modena

The four exhausts of Zonda have certainly become an icon of Pagani Automobili over time. Still, you won't believe where this concept comes from!

Come over and say hi, we'll be waiting for you in Piazza Grande, Modena.

Will it do the same to you? Come to find it out at the Motor Valley Fest!

Have you ever wondered how the four exhausts were born? Or even what inspired the shape of Huayra's side mirror? Stay tuned to find it out!
